summaries.short: In the Season 6A finale, Tony gets Carmela's career back on track; Chris picks up where Tony left off; A.J. gets a work perk.
summaries.full: In the Season 6A finale, Tony gets Carmela's career with the spec house back on track; Christopher picks up where Tony left off with Julianna, but it leads to dangerous ends; and A.J. becomes smitten by a young lady he works with. Meanwhile, Phil won't leave well enough alone, but medical troubles sidetrack him--prompting a surprising visit from Tony.
